{"tid":1520762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[暗黑兵法] 擾民責任　西環以外","createTime":"2019-08-31T03:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T05:09:18.000Z","uid":186,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"877ac349b13b216aab8fbade86573e55522d2e07","tid":1520762,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>西環以外　擾民責任</strong></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>封站為雙刃劍</strong></div></span></span><br />\n港鐵西營盤站一時半起關閉 列車不停該站。<br />\n手足仲要跟佢劇本到西環<br />\n擾民責任好容易就射左係示威者到<br />\n但示威者去到西環以外，禁封站影響民生，影響樓市嘅就會係黨鐵到。<br />\n<br />\n保民生，西環以外見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到西環叫口號又點，去哂十七區，慢慢封。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53685784639a617d67a088c094da21bb7d113498","tid":1520762,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"上一次　已經影響市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNOTQKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNOTQKz.jpg&h=1040c30f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/atfrrhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatfrrhW.png&h=68796a97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCJXxXY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCJXxXY.png&h=8f0641cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enrmZC1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenrmZC1.png&h=87373598&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4abeaeb299c08dea04efd7842017e2fcbd346d1","tid":1520762,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"十七區當立"},{"pid":"2f9a4a21b72c3f4adf8ed448d13317fe91747268","tid":1520762,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3224877/org/512a95db2c9638c56f72ab77036b58cc.jpg/9DLUi42QfnoOD2n3iCswxDBWCeDVFRSJ-yKS5fsikuU?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3224877%2Forg%2F512a95db2c9638c56f72ab77036b58cc.jpg%2F9DLUi42QfnoOD2n3iCswxDBWCeDVFRSJ-yKS5fsikuU%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=4890ab60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ccd84b41df3891222a1c657bce312932b7d9bf4","tid":1520762,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:07:15.000Z","msg":"港鐵今早10時許宣布，經風險評估並與政府相關部門溝通後，為保障乘客及員工安全，今日下午一時半起，關閉港島線西營盤站、列車亦不停該站，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵又提醒乘客，即使維持相關車站及列車服務，倘發生打鬥、破壞、其他暴力或大規模違反港鐵附例行為，而可能引致高風險或緊急情況出現，嚴重影響乘客及員工安全，來往個別車站列車服務亦有可能即時停止，且車站或在短時間通知或未能作事先通知情況下關閉。屆時將透過不同渠道例如港鐵網頁、車站及列車廣播等通知乘客。"},{"pid":"9eab433b6d1399dedda8259a46e73f089f2cf925","tid":1520762,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a4d66e201e773aa15f0afe7e7692e9cd11ef6d","tid":1520762,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab997334d4d5f7af3e21409d58404a1c5536405","tid":1520762,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854ce0c0c1e63c1798f9b47b65fc0572bdab6c84","tid":1520762,"uid":59804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:29:53.000Z","msg":"西環最新交通消息（